I have always hated beets. But hubby loves them. Since we met/married 6 years ago, our agreement has been that he try whatever I cooked. So, in fairness, I decided to try the beets in this recipe. Roasting made the difference. I must admit that it takes the total combination for me to like them, but it works for me. I will make this again.

